title: The 85 South Show Live In Cashvile Part 2 With DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & ChicoBean | Ep. 117
itunes:title: The 85 South Show Live In Cashvile Part 2 With DCYoungFly Karlous Miller & ChicoBean | Ep. 117
description:
Karlous Miller, D.C. Young Fly, and Chico Bean sold out two shows in Nashville and here in the second show its more of what they do best...roast, freestyle and talk their shit. D.C. Young Fly is hosting TRL everyday but he's got to get a roast session in. Karlous Miller is the star of Wild N Out and is always busting an old school freestyle vs. Chico Bean. At The 85 South Live Shows, they take it to a whole new level.
